## Layout

```
{{.ProjectName}}-meta/         # this directory (git-versioned)
{{.ProjectName}}/              # working copy (sibling, NOT a git repo at top level)
{{.ProjectName}}-<peer>/       # zero or more peer working copies, created via `mws clone`
```

## Conventions

- Edit harness content here, in the meta. Working copies see the change instantly through symlinks.
- New top-level files added directly in a working copy stay local until you `mws promote <path>` them.
- Native repos inside working copies are independent git clones -- each peer has its own `.git/`.
